              "name": "keycloak",
              "namespace": "dependencies",
              "notes": "Thank you for installing keycloak!\n\nRelease Name: keycloak\nNamespace: dependencies\n\nKeycloak has been deployed with the following configuration:\n\n1. Operator Version: 26.5.2\n2. Keycloak Instances: 1\n3. Realmtraefik\n\nAccess Keycloak Admin Console:\n  URL: http://keycloak.benchmarks.demo.traefik.ai\n  Username: traefik\n  Password: topsecretpassword\n\nOIDC Endpoints:\n  Issuer URL: http://keycloak.benchmarks.demo.traefik.ai/realms/traefik\n  Authorization Endpoint: http://keycloak.benchmarks.demo.traefik.ai/realms/traefik/protocol/openid-connect/auth\n  Token Endpoint: http://keycloak.benchmarks.demo.traefik.ai/realms/traefik/protocol/openid-connect/token\n  Userinfo Endpoint: http://keycloak.benchmarks.demo.traefik.ai/realms/traefik/protocol/openid-connect/userinfo\n  \nOIDC Client Configuration:\n  Client ID: traefik\n  Client Secret: NoTgoLZpbrr5QvbNDIRIvmZOhe9wI0r0\nConfigured Simple Users:\n  - user0@test.com@traefik.io (password: topsecretpassword)\n  - user1@test.com@traefik.io (password: topsecretpassword)\n  - user2@test.com@traefik.io (password: topsecretpassword)\n  - user3@test.com@traefik.io (password: topsecretpassword)\n  - user4@test.com@traefik.io (password: topsecretpassword)\n  - user5@test.com@traefik.io (password: topsecretpassword)\n  - user6@test.com@traefik.io (password: topsecretpassword)\n  - user7@test.com@traefik.io (password: topsecretpassword)\n  - user8@test.com@traefik.io (password: topsecretpassword)\n  - user9@test.com@traefik.io (password: topsecretpassword)\n\nTo verify the installation:\n  kubectl get keycloak -n dependencies\n  kubectl get keycloakrealmimport -n dependencies\n  kubectl get pods -n dependencies\n\nFor more information, visit: https://www.keycloak.org/\n",
